gomodel:SYNGO_2314  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 5: \"Colocalization of abLIM3 with synaptic markers in the mouse cerebellum.\"\n- Literal:\"(B) Higher magnification of images of the neocortical region of the cerebellum. Arrowheads indicate the colocalization of abLIM3 and VGluR1.\"\n\n28/12/2017 Pim\n- VGluR1 mentioned in the literal text by the authors should be 'VGluT1'.\n- VGlut1 is a glutamate transporter of synaptic vesicles and is a marker protein of presynaptic elements.. Experimental description: Fig. 5 Title: \"Colocalization of abLIM3 with synaptic markers in the mouse cerebellum.\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6893-6177" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5265-6306" ;
        dc:date           "2018-01-18" ;
